sentences: Cinder Block (born Cindy Morgan, May 13, 1961) is an American punk rock vocalist and visual artist.
Cinder sang for Fat Wreck Chords band, Tilt from 1992 to 2001.
Since 2018, she has sang for The Pathogens.
Cinder Block Inc. Cinder makes silkscreens and has been doing so for almost two decades.
